  "imageCount": 5,
  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598258961052-U1ST1OX7V9LGBFB8AOBB/14a-Amy%2BTangerine%27s%2Bdesk.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>As a contributor for <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico</a>, I only receive kits on occasion now. It was really freeing only having to do 1 small assignment, but at the same time I miss the joy in in having to document my memories with all the fun products on a monthly basis. And I missed the need to make a mess on my desk. I used the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/cirque-project-life-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Project Life kit</a> and <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/pantomime?aff=6cc2c70f\">Pantomime</a> for this one pager. I'm still working on filling in some (okay maybe a lot of) blanks for my 2014 album.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598258982840-4CDE15I0I0UV5GLMNGG7/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Decided I would have to have at least 1 spread or page that represents each month in the 2014 album. This will make it easier to fill in the blanks (I think). I definitely wanted to include the days we spent in Florida, even though it wasn't a complete week, and it went from a Friday to Wednesday in November. Since this page made sense to go chronologically after the Hello Kitty event, I had to use the back of <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/galleries/145328-hello-kitty-con\">this page</a>. For the square pockets, I intended on keeping it pretty simple. Instead of leaving the grey cardstock from my stash plain, I cut the card into strips and adhered it to fill in the sides next to the photo. With the other 2 cards, I added the washi tape on the sides. I love the way they turned out. The sunshine is from the adorable <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/spring-card-sticker-set-by-life-love-paper?aff=6cc2c70f\">Spring Card + Sticker Set by Life.Love.Paper.</a> - and the best part is that it's just $5.99. The script \"Time for new things\" card is part of that set too!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598258999697-5JY36CNTTDF26RUZQPUO/14c-IMG_7416.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598259019830-QZCQE1QEJXNG2QKR1NU1/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598259031143-ILNB1VJQHCB55WTY5Q77/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>So there you have it, a couple more pages to add to the 2014 album. How are you all doing on your memory keeping from last year? I think I am going to just fill in the blanks that I can and not stress about the rest. There's plenty of new memories to be made! Plus, if I feel it's important at a later time, I can always go back and do it. Who's with me?!</p><p>You can shop for all <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/cirque?aff=6cc2c70f\">Cirque kits here</a> and see <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/project-folders/6662-cirque?aff=6cc2c70f\">my projects here</a>.</p><p><em>Keep in mind that </em><a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/?aff=6cc2c70f\"><em>subscribers</em></a><em> can shop the pre-sale each month at noon EST on the 27th. Others need to wait until the clock strikes midnight tonight. </em><a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/?aff=6cc2c70f\"><em>Become a subscriber</em></a><em> and get in on all the benefits and rewards that </em><a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/?aff=6cc2c70f\"><em>Studio Calico</em></a><em> has to offer!</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}